column2:
While the Tatars have traditionally been our rivals and a barrier to Russian unification, some of them have taken up our cause and religion, including the Muscovite Temryukov dynasty. These 'Russo-Kryashens', as they are known, are a sure sign that we will be able to earn the loyalty of our Tatar subjects.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
integrate_astrakhani_culture_title;Integrate the Volga Tatars;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
integrate_astrakhani_culture_desc;The Tatars of Xacitarxan are very similar to those in Kazan, although rather more of them are Muslim. It will not take much more effort to integrate them into Russia.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
integrate_georgian_culture_title;Integrate Georgia;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
integrate_georgian_culture_desc;The Caucasus is full of small, bickering nationalities. Georgians are potentially useful to us for their legacy of Orthodox Christianity, and if we empower them, they may serve as a useful bulwark against Turkish aggression, or any other state that may arise in the Middle East.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
integrate_estonian_culture_title;Integrate the Estonians;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
integrate_estonian_culture_desc;We've been trading with the Estonians for quite a while. As long as we show some respect for their language and culture, we should be able to keep them from turning to Scandinavia or elsewhere for freedom.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
integrate_latvian_culture_title;Integrate the Latvians;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
integrate_latvian_culture_desc;Like the Estonians, we have interacted with Latvians for some time, and integrating them into our social fabric should be quite simple.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
integrate_finnish_culture_title;Integrate Finland;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
integrate_finnish_culture_desc;We can finish enforcing our hegemony over the Baltic by giving special consideration to the needs of the Finnish people. By doing so, we will create a strong and loyal buffer against any Scandinavian revanchism.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
moscow_expansion_steppes_title;The Wild Lands;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
moscow_expansion_steppes_desc;The Tsardom has competed with the Tatars for centuries and the areas along the Don and the Volga rivers have changed hands regularly. The current balance of power makes us a possible target of the Scandinavians through their puppet of Novgorod but should we rise again we could easily claim the Steppes as ours!;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
create_rossian_empire_title;For the Holy Russia!;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
create_rossian_empire_desc;The Empire of Holy Russia is a natural successor of the Tsardom of Moscow. We shall use the newly-gained power to bring Mother Russia to its former glory.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
mother_russia_calling_title;For Holy Russia!;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
mother_russia_calling_desc;The Empire of Holy Russia is a natural successor of the Tsardom of Moscow. We shall use the newly-gained power to bring Mother Russia to its former glory.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
claim_siberia_title;Go east, young man;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
claim_siberia_desc;The Siberian plains were claimed by the Russian rulers since the times of Vladimir Atlasov and Danila Antsiferov. We have to keep our word.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
form_batavia_title;Boer Unification;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
form_batavia_desc;Since the Boer Wars following the Great German Wars a new idea has spread amongst the Afrikaans people. More and more people are advocating for a new state to rise to unify the Boer States. This state will maybe be able to reclaim Kaap and maybe even threaten the European establishment;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
setup_decision_title;Setup;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
setup_decision_desc;This should never be read outside of a localisation file.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
form_lesser_germany_title;Form the Danubian Confederation;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
form_lesser_germany_desc;Our dominant position over the south and central German states is now firmly established. While it will still take time to unify all the Germans, today we can at last form a proper German kingdom - a stepping-stone to greater things!;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
