freeSER_title;Liberation of Serbia;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
freeSER_desc;Serbia is under our control. We have captured the forts along the Danube and penetrated deep into the Empire's territory. The Sultan will be forced to acknowledge our victory!;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
cyrenaica_TUN_title;Hafsid Cyrenaica ;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
cyrenaica_TUN_desc;We have successfully taken Cyrenaica from the Egyptian rebels. It is time to integrate it into our country.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
move_capital_to_ankara_title;Move Capital to Ankara;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
move_capital_to_ankara_desc;Ankara is home to the Turkish national movement, and a more defensible location away from European enemies.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
form_UAR_title;Unite All the Arabian Nations;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
form_UAR_desc;Under the long oppression by the Ottoman Empire the Arabians suffered. Now we stand united against the enemies of Islam once again!;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
claim_ethiopia_title;Project our Influence in Abyssinian Lands;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
claim_ethiopia_desc;Our Empire now stretches from Damascus to Tripoli, from Jerusalem to Mecca, from Ryiadh to Cairo. We can use our power and exert it over the weak kingdom of Ethiopia, that resisted many Funj invasions, but had to kneel before us.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
move_capital_to_cairo_title;To Cairo!;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
move_capital_to_cairo_desc;Cairo was the capital of the Fatimid, Ayyubid and Mamluk caliphate from 969 to the 16th century when it was conquered by the Ottoman Empire that moved the center to Istanbul. Let's return the former glory to this ancient city!;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
