United_syria_title;Syrian minorities;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
United_syria_desc;Greater Syria encompasses many cultures: the Arabs may be the more numerous but the Levant has several communities due to its status of crossroads. Currently the Druze and Syriac minorities are discrimanited despite them being an integral part of the Syrian people. We can remedy to this problem but it will alienate the most religious.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Kurds_Assyria_title;Assyrians and Kurdistan;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Kurds_Assyria_desc;The biggest minority in our state is the Christian Chaldean community, often named the Assyrians. Kurds and Assyrians have a long past of infightings, more often because of the Kurds than the latter. But as the rule of law becomes even more important in Kurdistan relations between both communities have become to improve and it seems that the Assyrians could really become an integral part of the new Kurdistan.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
claim_the_desert_title;Claim the Sahara;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
claim_the_desert_desc;The Sahara is immense and empty and forms a perfect frontier for our nation. However we should claim it before other nations take control of it!;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
claim_the_west_desert_title;The Western Sahara;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
claim_the_west_desert_desc;With our control of Morocco complete we should claim the western Sahara lands before any imperialists try to take control of these lands!;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
claim_tripoli_title;Claim Tripolitania;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
claim_tripoli_desc;With Maghreb under our control, we have to take control of Tripolitania to protect our brothers from the Imperialists!;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
organize_mauretania_title;Organize Mauretania;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
organize_mauretania_desc;We should organize the African colonies to better reflect both a local structure, as well as set up the possibility for autonomous rule-- dominated by our benevolent colonial administrators, of course.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
organize_numidia_title;Organize Numidia;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
organize_numidia_desc;Now that the Magrebi tribes were defeated we should reorganize our Maghrebi territories in a new colony. We must create the proper structures, so that it stands on par with our other national states.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
organize_libia_title;Organize Libya;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
organize_libia_desc;Now that we control Tripoli, we should reorganize our African territories in a new colony. We must create the proper structures, so that it stands on par with our other national states.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
end_the_merina_monarchy_title;End The Merina Monarchy;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
end_the_merina_monarchy_desc;Following a local uprising in 1897 France, who had long held Madagascar in its sphere of influence, formally deposed the Royal House and annexed the Island.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
pegu_treaty_title;Treaty of Pegu;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
pegu_treaty_desc;With the Burmese under our influence, we can attempt to annex the entire coast of Burma. They might not agree peacefully, though...;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
uniting_turania_title;Unification of the Steppe;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
uniting_turania_desc;The Steppes have seen the fall of many nomad empires: the Saka, the Xiongnu, the Mongols... All have faded and are now only remembered in history. But the Steppes need a leader to unite them into a single state, not a Khanate a relic of the past, and who will protect them from Imperialism, be it from Europe or Asia!;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
expanding_manchuria_title;Rescue the Manchus;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
expanding_manchuria_desc;The Manchus are closely related to our homeland. In fact if it were not for the petty Qing Empire they would have surely joined us. Japan has interests in the area and it is our duty to protect the Manchu from China and Japan alike. And an access to the sea would be interesting for our country...;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
form_usca_title;Form the United Provinces of Mesoameriga;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
form_usca_desc;The UPMA - one of the succesors of Gran Colombia - died as well. But we can ressurect on our path to the greater glory…;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
treaty_of_waitangiDVG_title;Treaty of Waitangi;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
treaty_of_waitangiDVG_desc;With our control over the Southern Island complete, we can now force the Maori to sign an unequal treaty with us;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
organize_new_zealand_title;Organize Australia;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
organize_new_zealand_desc;Our colonies in the Maori Islands are becoming a true part of the country. We must create the proper structures, so that they stand on par with our other national states.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
reorganize_new_zealand_title;Reorganize New-Zealand;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
reorganize_new_zealand_desc;We have taken the Maori islands and we can now reorganize the old colony of New-Zealand;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
accept_maoris_title;Accepting the Maoris;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
accept_maoris_desc;The New-Zealand colony is recent and the Maori tribes still represent a large part of our population. instead of oppressing them we should guarantee the rights given by the treaty of Waitangi to better integrate them into our social fabric.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
austral_destiny_title;Austral Destiny;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
austral_destiny_desc;For many years our people have dreamed of going back to the Middle Kingdom. But as we can see know Zuharra has truly become the centre of culture like our old homeland. We can now claim the Mandate of Heaven and rule over our previous tributaries!;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
accept_aborigine_title; Aborigine Integration;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
accept_aborigine_desc; Even if our culture is the best one we have come to acknowledge the valor of the primary people of Zuharra. It is time to recognize them and integrate them into state.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
accept_maori_title;Integration of the Maoris;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
accept_maori_desc;The Maoris people were the first people the new Treasure fleets encountered when our kings decided to spread their dominion across the Austral Seas. Now that we control the Eastern Islands we can recognize our old tributaries as an integral part of our culture;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
accept_melanesian_title;Integration of the Melanesians;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
accept_melanesian_desc;The Melanesian people are spread across the Northern Islands predominantly on the one called Papua. We have established ties during the Era of Expansion and now we fully control the territory occupied by these people we can integrate them into our ever growing state;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
assimilate_tributaries_title;Hamronize all Under Heaven;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
assimilate_tributaries_desc;Ever since the arrival of the first colonists from Zhongguo to Zhourao, our relation to the natives of the land has been one of tributary subjugation rather than outright domination, and the Aborigine have traditionally been allowed to pursue their barbaric way of life. However, if we want to compete in this new world and strengthen ourselves, we must enlighten the Hu people and bring them into the fold of Tianxia.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
poni_subjugation_title;Subjugation of Po-Ni;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
poni_subjugation_desc;Lanfang occupies only a small part of the island of Po-Ni, also known as Borneo by the Westerners. It is our duty to civilize the whole island and its people so they don't end up under the boot of the imperialists!;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
dayak_integration_title;Integration of the Borneans;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
dayak_integration_desc;The native people of Po-Ni, the Dayaks have better life conditions under our rule than under the Malays or the Westerners but it doesn't mean that they are our equal. With the development of our state we could improve their conditions and officially make them citizens of Lanfang!;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
purchase_spanish_pacific_title;Purchase the Spanish Pacific;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
purchase_spanish_pacific_desc;With the Spanish having lost their international power, their Pacific holdings appear now difficult to administrate and incredibly expensive. Considering that our government's interests lie in increase our possessions in the Pacific, we should perhaps approach them with the notion of purchasing these islands for ourselves.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Bastaards_SAF_title;The Bastaard Question;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Bastaards_SAF_desc;The Bastaard or Griqua people are descendants from Boers mixed with the locals and who moved on to form their own communities like in their republic of 'Vryland'. They suffer many discriminations in our country despite the fact that they are civilized and speak a better Afrikaner than the Burgundian settlers around Kaapstadt. If we can rally a significant political force to support reform we could make them proper citizens of our state.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
bring_it_on_title;Income Cuts;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
bring_it_on_desc;Due to the world being so generous towards less gifted nations of the world, we earn more fortune than we could possibly dream of. Maybe we should be less greedy?;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
bring_it_off_title;Restore Income;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
bring_it_off_desc;While it is nice being generous and all but to be honest, the playing field should be even.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
selon_treaty_title;Proclaim the Selon Treaty null and void;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
selon_treaty_desc;With Spain falling out of grace, we do not have to abide by the rules set by the Treaty of Selon anymore.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
secure_south_granada_title;End of Incan Claims;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
secure_south_granada_desc;The Quechua people inhabiting Granada have been pushing for reunification with the indigenous Incan Empire for centuries and often stage protests and revolts against our rule. But now with our power asserted amongst the powers of the World and our influence in the Incan Empire we can force the Quechua to relinquish any claims on our territory!;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
create_gendarmeria_title;Creation of the Gendarmeria Federal;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
create_gendarmeria_desc;The federal nature of our state poses serious problems for maintaining order, with the various police forces underfunded by the local authorities, lacking proper training and squabbling over jurisdictions. The central government has proposed the creation of a Federal Force inspired by European methods, the Federal Gendarmerie which will be able to act over our whole territory as to severely hinder the rebellious elements of our population.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
conquer_old_england_title;Claim Old England;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
conquer_old_england_desc;England has been reborn from the ashes but it isn't guided by the rightful King, ours who sits in Camelot. With our power we can claim the island for ourselves and impose our will on the English people!;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
English_southern_cores_title;Reclaim our cores!;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
English_southern_cores_desc;Our lands have been stripped from us before, but no longer! We have asserted our independence from the Dual Monarchy and will reclaim all of our english isles! Long Live $COUNTRY$!;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Beornian_Cone_title;The Amerigan Cone;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Beornian_Cone_desc;Beornia has battled for centuries with the Mapuche and the Incas for the control of the south of the continent. Rather than limit ourselves to the uncivilized pampas of the south we can also claim the southern Incan provinces, cross the Andes and claim the Pacific!;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
sponsor_transcontinental_title;Sponsor the Trans-Continental Railroad;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
sponsor_transcontinental_desc;The links between Porto Novo and Nova Lisboa are tenuous at best, and it is with great difficulty that people travel from one ocean to another in Lusitania. The advent of the railroads could alleviate this problem if we were to sponsor a company that would link the two cities and the two seas. It would moreover dynamize relations with Qingqiu in the West and the rest of Arcadia to the East.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
accept_SLO_title;Integrating Slovenia;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
accept_SLO_desc;The Slovenians are a South Slavic people, much like ours although their language is quite different from Croat. They are also Catholic, contrary to the Serbs or the Bosniaks. Making them accept our rule should not be difficult, even more so with the Austrian threat in the North.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
independent_SLO_title;Independent Slovenia;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
independent_SLO_desc;Slovenia is now in Slavic hands and the claims of the Germans on our territory are forfeit.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
croatian_compromise_title;The Croatian Compromise;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
croatian_compromise_desc;The Croatians had enjoyed a great deal of autonomy under the personal union with Hungary in the Middle Ages. Yet Croats and Magyars became separated in the aftermath of the Ottoman conquest, divided in Bohemian, Venetian and Turkish spheres of influence, and after liberation the upsurge in Magyar ethno-nationalism poisoned the relationship between the erstwhile brother peoples. The $YEAR$ Croatian-Hungarian Kiegyezés - Compromise - will rectify the current situation and acknowledge the long-standing tradition of self-government of Croatia within Hungary while recognising the status of Croatians as full citizens of our state and the Croatian language as co-official with Magyar.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Cuba_CLM_title;Join with Colombia;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Cuba_CLM_desc;We are independent but Gran Colombia still stands strong so it might be a better idea to join them.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
romanian_cherson_title;Romanian Transnistria;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
romanian_cherson_desc;The Dniester has never been a fixed border for the Romanian people with many Moldavians choosing to cross the river and establish themselves in various settlements. It is our duty to claim this territory to protect our brothers and increase our national territory.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
enabling_crisis_title;AI: Crisis Enabled;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
enabling_crisis_desc;Crisis are enabled.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
make_transcaucasia_coptic_title;Make Coptic Christianity the Official Religion in Transcaucasia;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
make_transcaucasia_coptic_desc;The Coptic minorities long have been oppressed in Transcaucasia. It's time to exert our power in Transcaucasia and put them in power so Transcaucasia religious policy is in unison with ours.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
PLA_upper_messipi_title;Claim the Upper Messipi;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
PLA_upper_messipi_desc;The Messipi is a crucial waterway for the economy of our country, vertebrating trade and transport on a south-north axis beggining in our capital, Nouvelle Orleáns, located on the delta. If we control direclty the upper course we will be able to extend our influence north-westwards, bringing a large territory in continental Arcadia under our control and pre-emting Lusitanian expansion into the area.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
PLA_messipi_basin_title;Claim the Sioux Hinterland;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
PLA_messipi_basin_desc;We now control most of the Messipi watershed, with only the lands far to the North inhabited by the Sioux resisting our rule. Although we already have relations with them through traders and missionaries, it is time to bring them closer into our fold, forcefully if necessary.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
VIN_gylhenvik_title;Claim Gylhenvik;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
VIN_gylhenvik_desc;Thea area around lake Finnjøn is divided between Rhønnst, Algonquin and Sioux tribes which are mutually hostile. For a long time we have mantained a policy of divide and rule to forward our interests, but now it might be time to directly occupy the area and establish formally our frontier with the Rønnst polity further west.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
VIN_tjorin_title;Claim Tjorin;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
VIN_tjorin_desc;In recent years reports from prospectors have shown region of Tjørin is rich in coal ore. Wrestling control of this land from the native Sioux tribes will allow us to establish coal mines and fuel our hungry industry;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
VIN_northern_lakes_title;Claim the Northern Lakes;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
VIN_northern_lakes_desc;The territories to the extreme North-West of our frontiers are inhospitable and largely uncharted except for a few major landmarks reported by fur traders. Although mostly frozen wastes, occuppying this area around lakes Blasjøn and Lillenhavet will give us control over large tracts of unclaimed land, ripe for prospecting.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
AMA_amazonian_basin_title;Claim the Amazonian Basin;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
AMA_amazonian_basin_desc;For years, the vast and largely unexplored amazonian basin has drawn adventurers from all over our country, driven by a promise of fortune. Now that we have the technology to establish long-distance communication, using the waterways to transport personnel and supplies, we can finally occupy the amazonian hinterland and its riches before other powers do so.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
AMA_amazonie_profonde_title;Claim Amazonie Profonde;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
AMA_amazonie_profonde_desc;Although we have established firm control over most of the Amazonian basin, the northernmost territories are still uncharted, the dense rainforest hindering settlement of colonists. Recent technological advances and, most importantly, the rise of rubber as a valuable commodity, have however made this region, previously thought to be economically barren, target for fortune seekers coming up the Amazon River. It is on our best interests to establish formal control over the area and exploit its resources.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
LOT_grand_chaco_title;Claim the Grand Chaco;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
LOT_grand_chaco_desc;The Grand Chaco lies on our eastern frontier, inhabited mostly by nomadic Guarani tribes. Although most of it is arid and unsuitable for agriculture, we have a formal claim on it since the 18th Century explorations by Burgundian missionaries, and we would to well to occupy it before other powers move in to encroach upon our frontiers.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
GAN_wencheng_title;Claim Wencheng;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
GAN_wencheng_desc;The Azhou peninsula lies north to our lands. Controlling it would give us access to fertile lands for farming as well as a commanding position in the Torres strait, making it a strategic possession.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
GAN_oodnatta_title;Claim Oodnatta;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
GAN_oodnatta_desc;The region of Oodnatta is mostly arid and unsuitable for agriculture, but the areas around the South-Eastern lakes and the southern coast have a much milder climate, making them targets for the settlement of Zhourao pioneers.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
GAN_noongar_title;Claim Noongar;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
GAN_noongar_desc;The areas around Noongar and Kojonup represent the most fertile land in the western coast of the continent. Bringing them under our control will be an important step in our expansion westwards, before foreign powers establish colonies that might threaten the integrity of our celestial realm.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
GAN_coomalong_title;Claim Coomalong;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
GAN_coomalong_desc;Establishing direct control over the Coomalong region will finally formalize our direct control over the entire seaboard of Zhourao. Heaven has led us west!;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
GAN_yolngu_title;Claim Yolngu;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
GAN_yolngu_desc;The climate in the region of Yolngu is harsh, but establishing premanent presence in the Northen coast would allow us to establish firmer trade links with Nusantara and its rich lands.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
GAN_pitja_title;Claim Pitjantjatjara;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
GAN_pitja_desc;The Pitjantjatjara desert is the last remnant of untamed land in our realm. Although dry, inhospitable and sparsely populated, establishing direct control would allow Zhourao prospectors to look for valuable resources.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
AOT_motu_timu_title;Claim Motu Timu;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
AOT_motu_timu_desc;Motu Timu, the island south of our great realm, is inhabited by various fragmented Maori tribes. It is time to formally occupy Motu Pari, before any colonial power decides to enslave our brothers to the south!;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
DNG_yicheng_title;Claim Yicheng;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
DNG_yicheng_desc;Traditionally our Eastern border has been delimited by the Great Eastern Mountain Range, except for its southernmost section, where the native Pueblo people still control land west of the cordillera. Recent reports by prospectors have pointed out to the presence of coal ore in the region, which if we control directly could be used to build up our industry.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
DNG_haikou_title;Claim Haikou;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
DNG_haikou_desc;Although in the past Qingqiuan polities have seen the Great Eastern Mountain Range as the natural border of our realm, in recent years the great plains beyond to the west have become enticing avenues of expansion. Formalizing our claim to the area would allow us to exploit its resources and prevent Easterners from encroaching upon our natural frontiers.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
DNG_yulin_title;Claim Yulin;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
DNG_yulin_desc;With the Great Eastern Mountain Range now fully in our control, it has become time to move our frontiers westward and establish a buffer zone against Easterner agression.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
DNG_baizehu_title;Claim Baizehu;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
DNG_baizehu_desc;The Baizehu region has been disputed for many years between us and the Rhonnst people, with neither side actually exercising direct control over the area. We must move first and establish a formal colony in the area!;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
DNG_tangwan_title;Claim Tangwan;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
DNG_tangwan_desc;Tangwan, the region immediately north to our northernmost settlements, has for many years attracted Qingqiuan settlers looking to participate in the lucrative fur trade. It might be time to formally occupy these lands, lest our competitors east or west steal our thunder.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
HHR_baizehu_title;Claim Baizehu;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
HHR_baizehu_desc;The Baizehu region has been disputed for many years between us and the Qingqiu people, with neither side actually exercising direct control over the area. We must move first and establish a formal colony in the area!;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
HHR_tjorin_title;Claim Tjorin;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
HHR_tjorin_desc;Traditionally an area of conflict between our Rhonnst brothers and Sioux and Angolquin tribes, the Tjorin region is now being threatened by Vinlander expansionism. We must move quickly if we are to secure our borders against western agression.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
HHR_torsmark_title;Claim Torsmark;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
HHR_torsmark_desc;Although sparsely populated, the Torsmark region is home to a significant Rhonnst population. We should establish firmer control of the area in hopes of deterring further western expansionism and exploitation of our kin.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
sahara_1807_title;Claim the Tessalit Oasis;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
sahara_1807_desc;The nomads of the Saharan desert have always been too trouble with not enough benefits to be kept under control. With the Great Powers quickly setting out to carve Africa, establishing proper borders and proper control of even remote regions becomes a necessity. We can  strike out a series of treaties to set up the Saharan frontier of our territories and eliminate any possibility of border conflicts in the Sahara.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
sahara_1813_title;Claim Agadés;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
sahara_1813_desc;Agadés has been for over half a millennia a crucial node in trans-Saharan trade, being the crossroad of caravan roads coming east from Kano, west from Timbuktu and north from Tripoli. Controling it would grant us uncontested control over the Tuareg people living in the surrounding region.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
sahara_1825_title;Claim Zouar;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
sahara_1825_desc;The nomads of the Saharan desert have always been too trouble with not enough benefits to be kept under control. With the Great Powers quickly setting out to carve Africa, establishing proper borders and proper control of even remote regions becomes a necessity. We can  strike out a series of treaties to set up the Saharan frontier of our territories and eliminate any possibility of border conflicts in the Sahara.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
option_disable_DVG_badboy_title;Disable Divergences Infamy Reduction;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
option_disable_DVG_badboy_desc;Disables the -0,4 infamy modifier for Great Powers and the -0,2 infamy modifier for the rest of countries. Not thoroughly tested, use at your own risk.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
invite_kongo_missionaries_title;Invite Catholic Missionaries;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
invite_kongo_missionaries_desc;While our nobility has accepted Catholicism a long time ago, many of our peoples still adhere to ancient animistic worshippings. Now we could invite missionaries again who, together with our educated children, could provide an effective education.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
kongo_empire_title;Proclaim the Kongo Empire;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
kongo_empire_desc;Our backwards brothers have not taken the same path as us. We must bring them into modernity, by force if necessary, to protect them from being exploited by foreign powers. After all, in the end we only have their best interests in mind and through our shared heritage we will be able to make that clear.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
integrate_congo_cultures_title;Integrate our Brothers;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
integrate_congo_cultures_desc;While we may not speak the exact same language, all the people in our nation share the same heritage. We should show them that we are brothers, divided only by archaic tribalist tendencies. By education and integration into the political system they will come to accept and cherish our benevolent empire.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
kongo_mining_title;The Wealth of our Lands;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
kongo_mining_desc;Our lands are not only fertile for food, but also rich in mineral deposits. We should invite experts from abroad that will help us tap into these riches.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
kongo_liferating_title;Building in the Jungle;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
kongo_liferating_desc;Now that we have the support of most of our people we should build infrastructure that will improve the lives of everyone.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
TAR_krymchak_title;Abolish the Baddal tax;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
TAR_krymchak_desc;The Krymchaks are our close cultural brethen, speaking a Tatar dialect with heavy Hebrew and Aramaic influence. Traditionally, even if not outright persecuted, their adherence to Judaism made them second-class citizens under Islamic Law, living in separate quarters and paying the Jizya infidel tax. Our recent secularisation process has abolished the Jizya, although in practice it has been replaced with the baddal-askari - a paid exemption to military service. It is finally time to remove this last vestiges of religious discrimination and embrace our Krymchak brothers.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
declare_permanent_jihad_title;Declare Permanent Jihad;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
declare_permanent_jihad_desc;With our Holy Cities and the majority of our religious brethren unified under one flag we can renew the century old idea of the Jihad. The infidels may not like it, but we know our path is righteous. We will not rest until every single one of our neighbours acknowledges the supremacy of Allah and Islam!;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
reclaim_montenegro_title;Reclaim the Karadag Vilayet;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
reclaim_montenegro_desc;Ottoman control over Karadag was never more than nominal, the Montenegrin tribes controlling the rugged and remote countryside. Now that our Sublime State has finally crushed the revolts and healed the scars of decades of Civil War, it is time to reestablish Ottoman rule in the Balkans, and establishing frim control of Karadag would secure our southern flank for further expansion west.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
reclaim_illyria_title;Reclaim the Bosna Eyalet;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
reclaim_illyria_desc;For centuries the Bosna Eyalet was the heart of Ottoman power in the Balkans, housing a substantial muslim population loyal to the House of Osman. In the chaos following the Civil War between Mustafa IV and Suleiman II, however, Croatian rebels managed to successfully stage an uprising and, after 5 years of bloody and unconclusive warfare, Suleiman eventually acquiesced to Illyrian Independence in the 1815 Treaty of Sarajevo. The very existence of Illyria is an insult to Ottoman honour and a reminder of the humiliations suffered during the first three decades of the century. With the Ottoman Monarchy once again on an upward swing, it is time to finally reclaim what's ours and avenge Sarajevo.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
reclaim_madjaristan_title;Reclaim Madjaristan;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
reclaim_madjaristan_desc;The conquest of Hungary was the crowning achievement of Suleiman the Magnificient, striking fear throughout Christendom and representing the high-water mark of Ottoman power and prestige in Europe. The House of Osman managed to hold on to this troublesome province for nearly three hundred years of intermittent conflict with the Bohemian and Jagiellonian monarchies, but it was the first of the Ottoman domains to break away during the fraticidal Ottoman Civil War in 1807. With our hold on the Balkans once more secure, we can finally turn our attention to the last rebellious province that escapes our rightful control and finally reverse the damage caused by the Civil War.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
integrate_crimean_culture_title;Integrate the Crimean Tatars;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
integrate_crimean_culture_desc;The Crimean Tatars had the most centralised state of all the Khanates in the Pontic Steppe and have opposed the fiercest resistance to Russian rule of all the peoples subjugated since the unification of the Tsardom. If we want to achieve long-lasting internal peace in the region we need to incorporate the Crimean Tatars into the Imperial bureaucracy and end the opression of Tatar culture and religious practice.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
sedentarize_khanate_title;Sedentarise the Khanate;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
sedentarize_khanate_desc;For millennia great nomadic Empires have risen and fallen, dynasties rising and fading into oblivion, but with a common political blueprint. The Khan would be the supreme authority of the Khanate, ruling over a warrior nobility organised in left and right halves of the Empire. While this ancient system has proven its fruits, it is now clear than in the present age it is unsufficient to keep the sedentary polities at bay, whose greater degree of centralisation has allowed them to encroach more and more upon the grazing lands of the Nomadic Confederations. We have no option then, but to bend against the wind of time, adopt a bureaucratic system of administration and sedentarise the different clans and tribes.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
make_lisboa_capital_title;Move the Capital to Lisboa;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
make_lisboa_capital_desc;Lisboa has been the neural centre of Spanish inter-oceanic trade ever since the establishment of the Empire, the port through which slaves, spices, sugars and other riches from Arcadia and the Indies reached the metropolis. The seat of political power, however, was kept in Madrid at the behest of the powerful Castilian nobility. Now that we have redefined our relation with our criollo brothers, we must move the capital to Lisboa and acknowledge the new inter-Atlantic nature of the Commonwealth.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
fredensborg_treaty_port_title;The Fredensborg Treaty Port;;;;;;;;;;;;;x,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
fredensborg_treaty_port_desc;The port of Fredensborg was part of the Scandinavian Empire until 1817, when the inter-tribal warfare in the Ashanti confederation spilled over into the European fort. Scandinavia, being embroiled in the Great German Wars, was unable to spare forces to assist its garrison in Fredensborg and in the end grudgingly had to accept Ashanti sovereignty over the area. Fredensborg would serve as an excellent outpost for further expansion into the Gold Coast and beyond.;;;;;;;;;;;;;x,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
reclaim_bradenburg_title;Reclaim Trans-Krusné;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
reclaim_bradenburg_desc;Following the dissolution of the Elbian Confederation and the recognition of independence of the League of Berlin, we were force to give up the territory north of the Krusné range, awarded to us after the victory of the Catholic League in the Imperial Wars of Religion of the XVII Century. This territory is home to a singificant Bohemian minority, and now that we have regained our strength, it would be in our right to reclaim them and bring the opressed Bohemians under our protection.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
ameriga_annex_equinoxia_title;Propose the Integration of Equinoxie into the Federation;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
ameriga_annex_equinoxia_desc;The Amerigan Federation has succeeded in bringing together in harmony Lotharingia and Antartique, but the Amerigan dream is incomplete, as the Equinoxean Republic still stands on its own. The Equinoxeans won their independence after a hard-won struggle against Amazonie, and many in the young republic are hostile to the idea of surrendering any inch of sovereignty. We will send an embassy, hoping to convince them that our Federation is one based on the foundation that all men are born equal.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Purchase_of_Aragonese_Italian_antilles_title;Purchase of Sant Jordi;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Purchase_of_Aragonese_Italian_antilles_desc;Aragon-Italy possesses a few islands in the Caribbean but in exchange for some money it could easily be passed to us.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Purchase_of_Catalan_antilles_title;Purchase of Sant Jordi;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
Purchase_of_Catalan_antilles_desc;The Catalans possesses a few islands in the Caribbean but in exchange for some money it could easily be passed to us.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
integrate_zanj_title;Integrate the Zanj;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
integrate_zanj_desc;The Zanj have a long and tragic history in our lands - shorn  from their homeland in the African shores of the Indian Ocean, then passed on by Arab traders throughout the Islamic world until reaching far-away Maghreb to toil in plantations under the always unforgiving sun. The European colonisation of Zanzibar put the slave trade in terminal decline, and now the advent of mechanized farming has put the final nail in the coffin. It would be in our best interests to integrate the Zanj into the fabric of our society and establish a new relationship based on equality.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
invite_courland_title;Propose the Integration of Kurland in the Confederation;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
invite_courland_desc;The Duchy of Kurland is the last remnant of the easternmost extremity of the Oostkolonisatie - the expansion of the Elbian people into pagan Slavic and Baltic lands in the wake of the Northern Crusades. Although the rural population is largely Latvian speaking, the economic, social and political elites are still Elbian, as well as much of the urban population in the capital of Mitau. The past centuries have seen an erosion of the independence of the Duchy, often becoming an unwilling participant in the Scandinavian-Polish conflict for supremacy in the Baltic. For the sake of the continued existence of the Elbian poeple in the east, they must be incorporated into the Confederation, by force if necessary.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
invite_latvia_title;Propose the Integration of Livonia in the Confederation;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
invite_latvia_desc;Livonia had been under Scandinavian domination ever since 1629, leading to a progressive decline of the Elbian nobility ruling from Riga. Tides have turned with the recent establishment of an independent, Elbian-led Livonian state, although its vulnerability in the face of Polish revanchism and Russian expansionism is evident. For the sake of the continued existence of the Elbian poeple in the east, they must be incorporated into the Confederation, by force if necessary.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
invite_baltenland_title;Propose the Integration of the Baltenland in the Confederation;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
invite_baltenland_desc;The Elbian people have experienced a Renaissance in the past decades. In the West, the shackles of Burgundian and Scandinavian domination have been broken with the proclamation of the Elbian Confederation. In the East, the long decline of the Elbian people since the Great Livonian War has been brought to an end and their position as Heerservolk is undisputed. The eastern Elbians, however, remain pygmies in the face of the larger, heavily militarised rivals on their southern and eastern frontiers. For the sake of the continued existence of the Elbian poeple in the east, they must be incorporated into the Confederation, by force if necessary.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
nee_oostkolonisatie_title;The New Oostkolonisatie;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
nee_oostkolonisatie_desc;For far too long the Elbian people in the Baltic have been subject to foreign powers, with the catastrophic Livonian Wars seeing the end of the Terra Mariana as an independent state. We must establish dominance in the region, incorporate the Eastern Elbians into the Confederation and break Polish and Scandinavian power in the region once and for all.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
form_baltenland_title;Baltic Destiny;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
form_baltenland_desc;After centuries languishing under Polish and Scandinavian rule, the Elbians have finally recovered their position as the dominant people in the Baltic. The Livonian State encompasses a large part of the territory of the old Düütsche Orden, yet a significant part of our Elbian brothers still live outside of our borders. It is time to declare ourselves to be the successors of the Terra Mariana of old, and expand the reach of Riga beyond Livonia into Prussia and Lithuania.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
latvia_rename_title;Rename Latvia;;;;;;;;;;;;x,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
latvia_rename_desc;Latvia rightfully rightfully $COUNTRY_ADJ$, and should use $COUNTRY_ADJ$ names.;;;;;;;;;;;;x,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
estonia_rename_title;Rename Estonia;;;;;;;;;;;;x,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
estonia_rename_desc;Estonia rightfully rightfully $COUNTRY_ADJ$, and should use $COUNTRY_ADJ$ names.;;;;;;;;;;;;x,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
lithuania_rename_title;Rename Lithuania;;;;;;;;;;;;x,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
lithuania_rename_desc;Lithuania rightfully rightfully $COUNTRY_ADJ$, and should use $COUNTRY_ADJ$ names.;;;;;;;;;;;;x,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
integrate_baltenland_title;Integrate Baltenland into the Confederation;;;;;;;;;;;;x,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
integrate_baltenland_desc;The state of the Baltenland was created under our auspices to protect the Baltic Elbians from Scandinavian and Polish oppression. It's association with the Elbian Confederation was loose on purpose - the Bohemian states within the confederation frontally opposed the incorporation of millions of non-Bohemian subjects that might undermine their leading position within the Confederation. Now that all of the Baltic Elbian lands are under our control, the Elbian political class is pushing increasingly for annexation of the Baltenland. Doing so would make us uncontested masters of the region, but could have devastating consequences on the homefront.;;;;;;;;;;;;x,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
reclaim_brandenburg_anhalt_title;Reclaim Brandenburg-Anhalt;;;;;;;;;;;;x,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
reclaim_brandenburg_anhalt_desc;Peace has finally been secured with the League of Berlin and the Bohemian people are masters of their own destiny once more. The Peace of Prague, however, was not satisfactory to everyone in Bohemia - some feel that the post-war borders, drawn on ethnic lines, exclude a large part of the territory that was historically part of the Crown Lands of Bohemia for centuries, and some of the cities contain significant ethnic Bohemian minorities. Now that we have reasserted our position in Europe, it is time to claim back what is rightfully ours.;;;;;;;;;;;;x,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
form_polynesia_title;Unite the Polynesians;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
form_polynesia_desc;Long ago, our people embraced the waves and spread themsleves throughout the seas. However it has become clear to us that with the rise of non-islanders roaming our regions, and the passiveness of our neighbors, it was up to our mantle to bring us together to whether the storm. Long live Polynesia!;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
pacific_rim_title;Embrace the Micronesians;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
pacific_rim_desc;With the Polynesian peoples united under one banner, it is now time to set our eyes on more ambitious horizons. We should strive to unite all Austronesian peoples, and become masters of the Pacific!;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
integrate_maori_title;Integrate the Maori;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
integrate_maori_desc;The Maori are the descendants of early Polynesian pioneers which landed a long time ago on the untamed shores of Aotearoa. Now that these lands are part of our realm, we should embrace the Maori as our cultural brothers and elevate their position within our society.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
iberian_cooperation_treaty_title;Perpetual Treaty of Iberian Friendship;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
iberian_cooperation_treaty_desc;Spain and Aragon have had a tumultous relationship for the past few centuries. Erstwhile allies against the Muslims while rivals in European affairs, recent decades saw the relationship threaten to turn to war. However, now that Spain's interests have shifted to focus on the New World instead of Europe, an opportunity has presented itself for both the Hispanic Commonwealth and Aragon to secure their Iberian borders and end any petty squabbles that may exist between the two powers. We are cousins by blood, there is no need for bloodshed. As long as Aragon agrees (and they should if our relations are cordial), we shall have peace on the peninsula as our two nations ally to defend the common interests, culture, and values we hold dear.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
AFS_turkmenia_title;Secure the Northern Border;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
AFS_turkmenia_desc;The harsh sands of the Kara-Kum have demarcated our northern border ever since the loss of Transoxiana to the Dzungar armies following the collapse of our Empire. If we are to reclaim our lost territories in Sogdiana and Khwarezm, we should first stake our claims and bring back Timurtash administration to the sparsely-populated Kara-Kum.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
TAR_renovate_xacitarxan_title;Renovate Xacitarxan;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
TAR_renovate_xacitarxan_desc;Xacitarxan has been one of the key political and comercial centres of the Pontic steppe since its foundation in 1460. Its age, however, is starting to show. In order to implement a modern transportation network and to eliminate potential sanitary problems, we can invest in a renovation of Xacitarxan to make it the true jewel of the Idel.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
end_kartveli_autonomy_title;End the Kartvelian Autonomy;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
end_kartveli_autonomy_desc;The Principalities of Imereti and Samtskhe are the last remnants of the once mighty Bagrationi realm, shattered in the early XVI Century after a series of Mongol and Turkoman invasions devastated the region and splintered royal authority. Subsequently passing under Iranian and later Ottoman suzerainty, we are the current overlords of the Georgians. Directly annexing the Principalities would be a step forward in centralising the Khanate, remove the restive Georgian nobility and give as direct access to the Black Sea ports.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
end_shamkhalate_title;Abolish the Shamkhalate;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
end_shamkhalate_desc;The Tarki Shamkhalate is one of the most venerable polities in the Caucasus, coming to dominate Dagestan and the north Caucasus from the political center of Tarki. Their strategic position allowed them to become powerbrokers between competing empires, being courted both by Shahs and Sultans. The Tarki Shamkhals have been our vassals since the collapse of Ottoman power in the Caucasus, proving to be useful in fending off Tatar incursions from the north. Now, however, that our state is centralising and abandoning its old feudal structures, the Shamkhalate is nothing but an anacronism that must be erased from the map.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
integrate_kumyks_title;Integrate the Kumyks;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
integrate_kumyks_desc;The Kumyk people are close cultural relatives of the Turkomans, both following Sunni Islam and speaking Turkic languages. Although traditionally the Kumys have had friendly realtions with us, the recent annexation of the Shamkhalate into our state has caused unrest as the Turkoman bureaucracy moves in and sidelines the local landholding aristocracy. In order to achieve harmonious relations, we must make an effort to integrate the Kumyks into the machinery of the state and prevent future outbreaks of violence.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
encourage_baku_refineries_title;Encourage Oil Extraction in Baku;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
encourage_baku_refineries_desc;Small-scale petroleum extraction has been carried out in the enviorns of Baku since the beggining of the century, although the primitive drilling technology has so far limited exploitation to only the shallowest of deposits, making agriculture still the prime economic activity of the region. Nevertheless, recent advances in drilling and distilling methods have made further exploitation possible. Should we invest in oil-well infrastructure - drills, pumps, tank cars, pipelines - we could certainly build a true petrochemical industry in the region.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
move_capital_baku_title;Move the Capital to Baku;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
move_capital_baku_desc;The seemingly inexhaustible fountains of petroleum springing from Baku's soil have brought great prosperity to the once backwater-town, turning it into our nation's foremost city. This great wealth is reflected in the illuminated streets, the schools, the villas of oil barons - which put our current capital in Shaki to shame. It would be in our best interest to move the seat of the government to the economic heart of the State.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
integrate_tats_title;Integrate the Tats;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
integrate_tats_desc;The Tats are the present-day descendants of the Persian subjects settled by the Sassanids in the Caucasian frontier to bolster the defenses of the Empire. Traditionally, Turkoman policy towards Tats has been one of assimilation, although they still represent a plurality in our Caspian provinces. Now that we have moved our capital to Baku, whose population is predominantly Tat-speaking, we should consider embracing the Tats into the bureaucracy of the state in order to administer more efficiently the new economic centre of the Caucasus.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
embrace_northern_caucasus_title;Embrace the Peoples of the Northern Caucasus;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
embrace_northern_caucasus_desc;Now that our domination of the Caucasus is complete, we should set about to extending our enlightened administration to the fractious and war-like pople that populate its northern foothills. From the Adyghe in the Taman, the Ossetians and Ingush on the Terek and the Avars in Dagestan, all shall be brought under the warm embrace of Transcaucasia.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
CIR_integrate_abkhaz_title;Integrate the Abkhaz;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
CIR_integrate_abkhaz_desc;The Abhkaz are our close cultural kin, and only foreign intervention - Georgian, Ottoman and finally Turkoman - have kept us appart. Now that we have finally liberated our Abkhaz brothers from the Kartvelian yoke, it is time to integrate them into our realm.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
overthrow_xacitarxan_title;Break the Tatar Yoke;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
overthrow_xacitarxan_desc;Turkic nomads have been the traditional enemies of the settled Adyghe tribes living in Circassia, the plundering being destructive enough to induce Adyghe polities to swear fealty to the competing Empires in the Caucasus - the Ottomans and the Timurtash. With both Empires in deep turmoil and unable to send expeditions north of the Caucasus, we have recently come to be dominated by the Xacitarxan Tatars. Now that we have regained our strength, it is time for the Adyghe people to overthrow the Xacitarxani overlords.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
CIR_integrate_karachai_title;Integrate the Karachai;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
CIR_integrate_karachai_desc;The Karachai are the last surviving remnants of the Kipchak incursions in the Caucasus in the XI Century. They have been traditionally relegated to marginalization by Adyghe society, living in isolation in the mountains of the Central Caucasus, where they have taken refuge since the destruction of Alania by the Golden Horde. If we truly want to modernise our state, we should make an effort to integrate the Karachai into the fabric of our society and treat them as first-class citizens.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
greater_circassia_title;The Legacy of Inal the Great;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
greater_circassia_desc;The Adyghe people have not know a period of greater power than that of Inal 'the Radiant' in the XV Century. Starting from a small chiefdom in the Taman, Inal came to unify the Circassian tribes, subjugate the Karachai, conquer Abkhazia and drive the Tatars back to the northern shore of the Azak. Although the power of Circassia would fade away in the following centuries, we are now in a position to reclaim the entirety of Inal's realm as rightfully ours.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
CIR_integrate_xacitarxani_title;Integrate the Xacitarxani;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
CIR_integrate_xacitarxani_desc;The Tatars have been the traditional enemies of the Adyghe people, with their frequent raids devastating the Circassian countryside. However, our recent aquisition of territories on the southern bank of the Azak has meant the incorporation of hundreds of thousands of Tatars into our Empire. For the sake of efficient and pragmatic administration of our realm, we must integrate them into Adyghe society.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
overthrow_shaki_title;Rebel against the Turkoman;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
overthrow_shaki_desc;The Shaki Turkoman are the latest in a long list of foreign rulers to claim overlordship over the martyr lands of Georgia. The rise of the Shaki Khanate, following the end of Ottoman authority in the Caucasus, ended the brief spell of independence we enjoyed after the beggining of the Janissary Revolt and the Civil War that would engulf the entire Eastern Mediterranean. It is time to take destiny into our hands and stop paying tribute to the Turkoman, as a first step in re-uniting the Kartvelian people - even if will likely mean war with the Khan.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
unify_georgia_title;Unify Georgia;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
unify_georgia_desc;The ancient lands of Georgia are finally once again united after more than four centuries of infighting, foreign invasion and subjugation. The Georgian people can finally look at the future with hope - no longer will the fruit of their labour fill the coffers of Oriental Despots, no longer will the lands they till become battlegrounds between competing empires, no longer will their sons be levied for military service in struggles alien to Georgia. It is time to finally declare ourselves to be lords over all of Georgia.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
greater_georgia_title;Reclaim Queen Tamar's Realm;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
greater_georgia_desc;The reign of Mepe Tamar marked the zenith of Georgian political power and cultural splendour in the XIII Century. Stretching from the Sea of Pontus to the Sea of Gurgan, from Speri to Darband, her Kingdom became the dominant polity in the Caucasus, liberating the Armenian christians from Türkmen opression, vassalizing the erstwhile threatening Shirvanshahs and installing the Komnenoi as Autokrats of Trebizond. Now that Georgia has been reborn and is again a rising power in the Caucasus, it is within our rights to reclaim Tamar's realm and bring about a new Georgian golden age.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
GEO_integrate_armenian_title;Integrate the Armenians;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
GEO_integrate_armenian_desc;The Georgian and Armenian peoples have close cultural and religious ties, and together have suffered the indignities of Seljuq, Mongol, Ottoman and Timurtash rule. Already in the XIII Century the liberation of Armenia was a focal point of Georgian foreign policy which could never be fully realised. Now that we have liberated our Armenian brothers for good, we should recognise them as our true equals.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
reclaim_cyprus_title;Take Control of the Islands;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
reclaim_cyprus_desc;Cyprus and Crete are important strategical outposts in the mediterranean. With them being positioned so close to our homeland we can not allow any rivals to control these islands any longer.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
reclaim_shirvan_title;Reclaim the Shirvan and Tebriz Eyalets;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
reclaim_shirvan_desc;The Caucasian frontier was a source of constant tension throughout the history of the Ottoman and Timurtash Empires, the two neighbours coexisting in a state of latent hostility punctuated by jolts of violent, large-scale warfare for mastery over the greater Transcaucasian region. Although control over the region fluctuated with the fortunes of war, for the better part of two centuries the Ottoman state controlled Gorjestan and the Van Eyalet, whereas the Timurtash held a firm grip on a series of vassal Khanates stretching along Azerbaijan, Arran and Armenia as far west as Erivan. With our final victory over the Timurtash, these lands came under under our domain, organized in the Shirvan and Tebriz Eyalets, although they would be ultimately lost in the chaos of the Civil War. Now that Ottoman fortunes are on the rise again, it is time to reclaim what we rightfully won after our titanic struggle with the Timurtash.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
treaty_of_bandar_abbas_title;The Treaty of Bandar Abbas;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
treaty_of_bandar_abbas_desc;It was not so long ago that we were forced to sign a humiliating treaty to cede Qeshm to a foreign power - yet here we stand, our flag defiantly flying above the dilapidated Red Stone Fort after having expelled the Western invaders and repelled attempts to land along our coastline. We are now in a position to force the Europeans to the negotiating table, to return the Straits of Hormuz back to Iranian suzerainty and restore our national pride and dignity.;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
settle_iranian_nomads_title;Force the Tribes to Settle Down;;;;;;;;;;;;x,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
settle_iranian_nomads_desc;The tribes in Fars and the Zagros have traditionally enjoyed great autonomy within our realm, charged with the local administration of vast tracts of lands. Their migrational lifestyle prevents the full economic exploitation of the areas presently under nomad control, and it is clear that only by force will we be able to sedentarise them. We should establish the Tribal Affairs Office to register the land, block key mountain passes used for transhumanism and finally settle down the tribes as farmers and herders.;;;;;;;;;;;;x,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
reform_iranian_tribal_army_title;End the Tribal Domination of the Army;;;;;;;;;;;;x,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
reform_iranian_tribal_army_desc;The Shekhbizin Empire has its origins in a tribal coalition that arose to drive the Ottomans out of Luristan and this basic structure - tribal contingents coalescing around the authority of the Shekhbizin Shah - has remained largely unchanged ever since. The army is the most powerful social grouping in our realm, and its tribal Kurd, Lur and Qashqai components have shown obstinate resistance to any attempt at reform that would incorporate the urban Persians into it - and therefore diminish their share of power. If we are to field truly modern armed forces, tribal domination must end, even at the risk of sparking revolt in the lands of the Lur Ilkan and Qashqai Ilbeg.;;;;;;;;;;;;x,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
shekhbizin_basra_title;Reign in the Montafeq Arabs;;;;;;;;;;;;x,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
shekhbizin_basra_desc;The once splendourous city of Basra is now but a backwater port in the mouth of the Satt al-Arab river, suffering from centuries of negelct ever since the decline of the Abbasid caliphs. Nevertheless, incorporating Basra formally into our realm would allow us to stop the raids of the Montafeq tribe, currently sovereigns over the area, into our Khuzestani provinces. Additionally, the strategically located port would allow us to supress piracy and project power across the Persian gulf.;;;;;;;;;;;;x,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
shekhbizin_mazun_title;The Conquest of the Arabian Littoral;;;;;;;;;;;;x,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
shekhbizin_mazun_desc;Qatif and Bahrain, on the southern shore of the Persian Gulf, have for a long time being a point of dispute between Iranians, Turks and local Arab dynasties. The economic importance of the region has been on decline for centuries, its ports now mostly bypassed by merchant shipping. These ports, nevertheless, are still strategically located to act as points of resupply of fresh water on an otherwise arid coast, and are used as safe havens for pirates preying on the Iraq-India trade. After our conquest of Basra, exerting direct control over these ports would be the next logical step towards asserting dominance in the Persian Gulf and ending piracy once and for all.;;;;;;;;;;;;x,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
organize_habesh_title;Organize Habesh;;;;;;;;;;;;;x,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
organize_habesh_desc;We should organize the African colonies to better reflect both a local structure, as well as set up the possibility for autonomous rule -- dominated by our benevolent colonial administrators, of course.;;;;;;;;;;;;;x,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
