organize_angola_desc;Vestpost is becoming a true $COUNTRY_ADJ$ colony. We must create the proper colonial structures, so that it stands on par with our mainland provinces.;;;;;;;;;;;;;x,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
